data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous custom build located in peaceful Boulder Ridge Country Club gated community. Entertainers dream with so much sunlight! 1st floor features beautiful foyer, formal living formal, dinning room, sun room, sitting room,family room , Office,half bath, laundry room/ mud room and 3.5 car heated garage. 2nd floor offers 4 bedroom 3 full bath. You will fall in the love with the huge Master suit. Plenty of space to relax with sitting room and amazing master bath. 3 of the 4 bedroom have a exit to a  veranda overlooking backyard. This house doesn't stop there. The basement is finished with 2 bedrooms ,1 full bath, media room, flex room and Jacuzzi!!Basement would be perfect for in-laws. The Yard is so peaceful with trees and a secret garden!!!  This Home is the perfect place for entertaining so much room!! Would be a great for Multigenerational Family.  New roof 2022 with anchors, new washer and  dryer 2022, new dish washer,  new water heater 2023,Newer furnace and AC.
